# kubernetes :::: Container Orchestration Platform

Containers :::: that is help to run enviorment and spin app in isolated env over docker or smilier.

Docker podman Nomad ---- container spin 

--- swarm HA , entrprise application , service discovery or multi managent 

Orchestration refers to the coordination and management of complex, automated IT systems, applications, and services to streamline workflows. 

Kubernetes is a portable, extensible, open source platform for managing containerized workloads and services that facilitate both declarative configuration and automation. It has a large, rapidly growing ecosystem. Kubernetes services, support, and tools are widely available.

- Enchaned level Networking 
- Self Healing method 
- service Discovery and Load Balancing 
- scaling contianers and pods in Horizonatal 
- without changing conf or remove container update and rollback your services 

